===Verb===
'''бздеть''' (bzdet’)

#(''vulgar'') to [[fart]]
#: {{RUchar|[[фу|Фу]], [[кто]] набздел?!}} —&nbsp;''[[ugh|Ugh]], who's farted?''
#(''slang'') to be [[scared]] ''or'' [[afraid]] of something, to [[panic]]
#: {{RUchar|[[не#Russian|Не]] бзди, [[прорываться|прорвёмся]]!}} —&nbsp;''Don't panic, we'll break through!'' (Used as humorous encouragement in any situation, not necessarily when there is something to break through.)

